    {
      "id": "s001",
      "text": "Lesson 13.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "第13课。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s002",
      "text": "The Greenwood Boys.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "绿林少年。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s003",
      "text": "First listen and then answer the question.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "听录音，然后回答问题。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s004",
      "text": "Why will the police have a difficult time?",
      "translation": {
        "text": "为什么警察将会很难维持秩序？"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s005",
      "text": "The Greenwood Boys are a group of pop singers.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“绿林少年”是一个流行歌手组合。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s006",
      "text": "At present, they are visiting all parts of the country.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "目前，他们正在全国各地巡回演出。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s007",
      "text": "They will be arriving here tomorrow.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他们明天就会到达这里。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s008",
      "text": "They will be coming by train and most of the young people in the town will be meeting them at the station.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他们将乘火车来，镇上的大多数年轻人会到车站迎接他们。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s009",
      "text": "In the evening, they will be singing at the workers' club.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "晚上，他们将在工人俱乐部演唱。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s010",
      "text": "The Greenwood Boys will be staying for five days.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "“绿林少年”将在这里逗留5天。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s011",
      "text": "During this time, they will give five performances.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "在此期间，他们将演出5场。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s012",
      "text": "As usual, the police will have a difficult time.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "和往常一样，警察将会很难维持秩序。"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "s013",
      "text": "They will be trying to keep order. It is always the same on these occasions.",
      "translation": {
        "text": "他们将设法维持秩序。这种场合总是如此。"
      }
    }
  ],
